title: Career Education Day Introduces Students to Wentworth Programs (Wentworth Institute of Technology)
text: ( Source : Wentworth Institute of Technology ) October 14 , 2015 Michael MacPhail presents to a group of visiting students Nearly 200 high school students attended Wentworth Institute of Technology's first Career Education Day on October 5 .
